I bought a LOOKO2 sensor. The more expensive for PLN 950. I like Polish solutions and I support them. But every day I am thinking more and more about the correctness of this air quality sensor. I have already written to the boys a dozen e-mails with proposals for solutions and amendments. And new ones are coming out every day.  I am an electronics technician, so I was happy to look at the "inside" of this Polish electronic thought. The whole works under the control of a simple but giving the possibilities of ESP8266. Simple voltage stabilization, programming connector, RGB diodes signaling the air condition (4 pieces shine all in the same color, I will write further why) and a connected sensor of suspended particles. It is he who measures PM 1, 2.5, 10, formaldehyde levels, temperature and humidity.  And the first thing is that the temp / humidity sensor is inside the module. And therefore, the indications refer to the climate inside the box rather than outside. My phone shows -2C, car -3C, and LookO2 ... 12C :-)  HCHO level. For the first few days, these indications were not supported at all by their website, the API was not even variable. It appeared on Friday. Indication: stable 0. No one knows what, whether particles per million or something else. It's just zero. Only that zero is probably not possible in our time. WHO has determined 0.05ppm as the upper norm, 0.03 reportedly being "all the time" in the air. Well, as it shows 0 it probably is zero :-) Like 12C :-)  RGB LEDs - show a good state of air according to the CIEP's findings. Cool! You do not really need to go on the web, just look at the sensor and you already know. Diode is 4 pcs, all are lit at once. I wondered why anyway. I have read the warranty and have already learned: "Damage to one, two or three diodes is not covered by the warranty." The record is of course unimportant in accordance with the law (I would advise the boys to remove it so that someone would not cross and did not send to the OCCP), otherwise to undermine the simple non-conformity of the goods with the contract. After 5 days of use with 4, only one lamp shines: -0 Someone did not want to calculate the resistance on the diodes.  I'm cheering as much as I can, but I lose some of my hope from day to day that they may be able to stay longer. It's a pity, because Airly's typically Krakow policy does not suit me so much that I would not buy this solution.  #smog #electronics #industry show all   +: Health-oriented, slavas +2 others

Some time ago I came to my hometown for a moment. I passed the fuel depot and the whole neighborhood was covered with biting, yellow smoke. At first I wanted to call the municipal police, but I decided that I would not do it.  Instead of complaining to the authorities right away, I decided to take the oil lamp - I went to the guy and fucked him, that he was stalking us all, that he smoked the whole area, and you can see that he sells wet coal. I was expecting a foch, but the guest asked "what should I do?" I made him an accelerated course of smoking from the top and the benefits of this resulting (both health and economic). The guy grabs what I mean in the flight - almost as quickly as if he just wanted to blow me up. I knew that I would come back that way in 20-30 minutes and if he continued smoking then I would report it immediately.  It somehow happened that I was going past but after about 5-10 minutes. And to my great surprise I saw that only a light balloon comes out of the chimney, and the area has already vented. I was there several times over several days and there was no smoke every time. The guest is probably also now educating their clients, which makes the whole area less crowded.  So, Mirki, I encourage you to sometimes take matters into your own hands before the police or city guards do it. The mandate probably would not teach him anything, and thanks to that, the inhabitants of the area breathe more pure air.  #czujedobrzeczel #chwalesie #smog #bojowkapaleniaodgory  show photo spoiler not mine  show the whole source: wykop.pl   +: Secretary J.0, Pro-healthy +12 others

Photograph taken by the Italian austronaut Paolo Nespoli from the space station's deck. It shows the Po plain in a specific period. It was autumn. For almost 50 days it was not raining, foggy days and high inversion of temperatures, an orographic trap on three sides, and a drop in temperature by several degrees during the day, contributed to the concentration of pollutants in the cities of northern Italy, which was record high. Milan, Padua, Turin, Verona and Modena suffered from smog. Northern Italy is not accustomed to sudden and prolonged temperature drops. Everyone is heating up and the stone walls require to be heated intensively. The Italian authorities have decided to reduce the heating of municipal housing from 21 to 18 degrees. The difference is considerable. Cars with diesel (although it is known that they are not the main factor in the formation of smog) are often prohibited to enter the city every other day. As in #wroclaw today some gigantic smog, and the problem is still being downplayed by some, I will re-write the text about my adventure with smog, because with me it's getting better :)  One can say that I was very skeptical about the problem of smog. Not that I did not believe in its destructive properties, but what else to hear and read "leftist sources" and yet another thing to see and find out for yourself - nota bene literally.  It so happened that I am a man with quite poor health, since I have been struggling with quite an intense allergy, and for almost a decade with serious kidney disease. Recently, it has been very poor - less and less disease taking on drugs, more and more extensive destruction of the kidneys, increasing hypertension and a general feeling of well-being. Not to mention skin problems, they have always been.  It so happened that in August I went to study in Denmark. And you know what? I feel just sensational - the pressure went down just below the level of "perfect" which was still inconceivable in my case some time ago, research is coming out better and everything seems to indicate that the disease may not have been cured, but it has been severely inhibited. The last days in Poland hurt me so much that it rarely happened that I would not take anything painkiller for the night, but nothing here. But the most tangible effect of this change is zero body snot on August. The skin just healed me.  Also shocking for me was the first return to Poland where it was just SMOKING and I was seriously thinking about buying an anti-smog mask. After a few hours I got used to it and it did not bother me that much. The second return was much better and I did not feel such a change, but my sister also told me that I had just arrived at the moment when everything was dispelled by these hurricanes. I am far too distressed for my own country, especially with some "leftist" color but unfortunately this is the truth - Poland is a smelly poison of Europe and something must be done about it.  I realize that not all smog must be destructive - just like smoking, some people smoke for the rest of their lives and they are all right. However, you must bear in mind that if today you do not mind, it does not mean that tomorrow you will not get sick. And then every factor matters, especially in which air you are submerged.  Of course, I did not leave because of health, it all happened quite by accident, but unfortunately I have no intention of returning to Poland in the near future permanently because it simply means suicide for me.  #smog #polska #medycyna #neuropa # 4konserwy show whole   +: s_t_u_l_e_j, Emulsion +30 others

KZK GOP, MZKP Tarnowskie Góry and MZK Tychy are introducing on 07/02/2018 (Wednesday) free travels for passengers who will have their registration car with them on their journey. One more person who accompanies the registration certificate holder will also be able to use the free-of-charge option.  The reason for the announcement of free trips is the forecasted very bad air quality over the area of ​​cities and communes of the Upper Silesian-Zagłębie Metropolis.  Free rides will also apply to the trains of the Silesian Railways - with the exception of train connections between Chałupki - Bohumin and Ornak, running along the Żywiec - Zakopane section.  People who have proof of registration do not have to be formally the owner (entered in the registration document) to use the free ride.
